Type of Feat: Class
Prerequisite: Hospitaler level 1.
Specifics: Every level except 1st, 5th and 9th level, the hospitaler progresses in one selected divine spellcasting class. If a character had more than one spellcasting class in which he could cast divine spells before he became a hospitaler, the player must decide which class to assign each level of hospitaler for the purpose of determining spells per day and spells known.
Use: Automatic.